pay((bytes32,uint256,uint16,uint256,uint.details: Executed by the buyer, who relays the MetaTX with the operator's signature.  The buyer must provide the correct amount via msg.value.  If all requirements are fulfilled, it stores the data relevant  for the next steps of the payment, and it locks the funds  in this contract.
